<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.6">
<l>centaḻalē vantaḻalaic ceytiṭiṉuñ ceṅkamalam</l>
<l>antarañcēr veṅkatirōṟ kallā lalarāvāl</l>
<l>ventuyarvīṭ ṭāviṭiṉum viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāvuṉ</l>
<l>antamilcīrk kallā lakaṅkuḻaiya māṭṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if the red fire itself comes [and] makes heat,</l>
<l>the red lotus will not blossom except for the hot sun in the sky.</l>
<l>Even if You do not destroy severe grief, O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu,</l>
<l>I will not [have] my mind melt except for Your endless excellence.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
